      <title>赞比亚向消费者寻求增加太阳能发电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/zambia-turns-to-consumers-to-add-solar-power-generation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚将于 8 月 1 日启动一项计划，允许电力客户将电力输入国家电网，以增加供电并鼓励增加太阳能电池板的使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/zambia-turns-to-consumers-to-add-solar-power-generation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
