    <item>
      <title>美国计划在未来几个季度内保持票据和债券销售稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-plans-to-hold-note-bond-sales-steady-for-several-quarters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部连续第二次维持季度长期债务发行量不变，并维持其指导方针，即预计在“几个季度”内不需要增加票据和债券的发行量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-plans-to-hold-note-bond-sales-steady-for-several-quarters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦吉盈利因丰收而缩水至疫情期间水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/bumper-harvests-drive-earnings-miss-for-crop-trader-bunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球大丰收导致邦吉全球公司利润缩水，农作物市场低迷导致该公司今年剩余时间的业绩“前景不明朗”。股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/bumper-harvests-drive-earnings-miss-for-crop-trader-bunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:27:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士股市 13 个月内第二次停电，停市数小时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士证券市场运营商周三因技术故障无法发布定价数据而暂停股票交易数小时，这是该交易所有史以来最长的宕机，也是一年多以来第二次宕机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯领导人被杀再度引发地缘政治风险，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称以色列杀死了其政治领导人，此举加剧了该地区（该地区原油产量占全球三分之一）的紧张局势，导致油价出现自四月份以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
